A Black platebody (h5) is an item obtained from easy Treasure Trails. All of the black heraldic platebodies have the same stat bonuses as the black platebody. As with all Treasure Trails and Black armour, this cannot be made with the Smithing skill. It requires 10 Defence to equip.
